你能够调用以下的API:
[['RealEstateSearch.find_listings', {'name': 'RealEstateSearch.find_listings', 'description': 'This function searches for real estate listings based on type, location, number of bedrooms, and nearby amenities.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'type', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of real estate listing, e.g., rent, sale.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the listing is.'}, {'name': 'bedrooms', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of bedrooms in the property.'}, {'name': 'nearby', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'Amenities nearby, e.g., bus_station, subway.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'listings', 'description': 'A list of up to four matching listings, each with an ID, type, location, and bedrooms.'}]}], ['RealEstateSearch.get_listing_details', {'name': 'RealEstateSearch.get_listing_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific real estate listing given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'listingId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the real estate listing.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the listing, including orientation, price, and availability.'}]}], ['RealEstateSearch.get_community_info', {'name': 'RealEstateSearch.get_community_info', 'description': 'This function retrieves information about the community where a real estate listing is located.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'communityId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the community where the listing is located.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'info', 'description': 'Information about the community, including security, amenities, and management.'}]}], ['RealEstateSearch.get_tax_details', {'name': 'RealEstateSearch.get_tax_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves tax details for a real estate listing.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'listingId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the real estate listing.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'taxes', 'description': 'Tax details for the listing, including who pays property taxes and other fees.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `RealEstateSearch.find_listings` 并传入 `type`、`location`、`bedrooms` 和 `nearby`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "RealEstateSearch.find_listings",
    "args": "{'type': 'rent', 'location': 'Beijing', 'bedrooms': 3, 'nearby': 'bus_station'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
